Analyze Your Data

Salesforce Analytics Tools include Reports and Dashboards, Data Cloud Reports and Dashboards, CRM Analytics, Intelligent Analytics Apps, Tableau, Unified Analytics Experiences, Einstein Discovery.

Jumpstart Solutions with Model Templates provide out-of-the-box solution starter kits that can be customized to your solution requirements. Model templates are designed to integrate seamlessly with Salesforce data and handle tasks such as building the initial training dataset, creating a data pipeline, generating the first model, deploying it into Salesforce, and getting predictions on your data.

Maximize Customer Revenue Model Template: Use a linear regression model to predict which accounts could bring additional revenue based on sales over 365 days.

Maximize Win Rate Model Template: Explore key drivers for winning deals without prepping data.

Minimize Time to Close Model Template: Understand factors that drive shorter deal cycles without setup hassle.
title: Jumpstart Solutions with Salesforce Templates
